history.proof: intros K V K_eq_dec k v l H. induction l as [|x xs IHl]. -- simpl in H. discriminate. -- simpl in H. destruct x as [k' v']. destruct (K_eq_dec k k') as [Heq | Hneq]. ++ inversion H. subst. left. reflexivity. ++ right. apply IHl. auto.
